@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Processing
Processing --> Archived : confirm
Archived --> Approved : submit
Approved --> Draft : confirm
Approved : entry / log route
Draft --> OnHold : review
OnHold --> Created : confirm
OnHold : entry / log route
OnHold --> Draft : revert
Created --> [*]
@enduml